===Verb===
'''to use''' ('''uses''', '''used''', '''using''')

#''(transitive)'' to [[employ]] or [[apply]]
#:''Use this knife to slice the bread.''
#''(intransitive)'' in the past tense ('used') before 'to' to indicate a previous state
#:''I used to enjoy swimming.''

